title: Personal Paradise
description:
In a not too distant future, cities are controlled by government guided youth gangs. Those who are not in a gang are marked as outsiders. The silent and mysterious Julian is one of these outsiders, as well as the beautiful Anna. After Julian saved Anna from a beating at the hands of a gang, the story starts...

Note: This is not an OEL!
Note: This manga is not sold under age restrictions!
